{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0729f11c-1800-4a3a-ab29-d28363ab4399","content":"The directory appears empty. This is a general guidance question rather than a repo-specific task, so here's the migration path:\n\n### Migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n**1. Update your test project (`*.csproj`):**\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**2. Replace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` in your pipeline YAML:**\n\n```yaml\n# Before (VSTest@3)\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testSelector: 'testAssemblies'\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**\\*Tests.dll'\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After (dotnet test with Microsoft.Testing.Platform)\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run Tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: 'test'\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n**3. Publish results & coverage:**\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish Test Results'\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: 'VSTest'\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n  condition: always()\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish Code Coverage'\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n**Key notes:**\n- `--logger trx` preserves your TRX reports.\n- `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` keeps coverage collection.\n- Use `condition: always()` on publish tasks so results appear even on test failure.\n- If using Coverlet instead of the built-in collector, add the `coverlet.collector` NuGet package and use `--collect:\"XPlat Code Coverage\"`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7cc6c521-b336-4831-bd00-0206f81b43e3","outputTokens":537,"requestId":"5C23:31910B:A98C1:D4FBD:69F54B30"},"id":"3d20bb08-6395-44cc-b792-db8491596243","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:54:18.583Z","parentId":"103feec4-d445-4ed2-b337-4d93f89fdcb9"}
